welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Lower Bicutan, Philippines! Get ready to experience the charm of this city known for its rich culture, delicious food, and warm hospitality. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that our beautiful city has to offer."

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The oldest and largest terminal at Ninoy Aquino International Airport, serving both international and domestic flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: Also known as the Centennial Terminal, it primarily serves international flights for Philippine Airlines.

terminals.name: Terminal 3
terminals.description: The newest and largest terminal, serving both international and domestic flights for Cebu Pacific and other airlines.

terminals.name: Terminal 4
terminals.description: Also known as the Domestic Terminal, it serves domestic flights for smaller airlines such as AirAsia and Cebgo.

wifi.note: The WiFi is free for the first 2 hours, after which it requires a purchase of a voucher.
